{"url":"http://www.seisou-center.co.jp/company/","html":"<!doctype html>\n<html lang=\"ja\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n<title>企業情報 | 株式会社　清掃センター｜青森県八戸市</title>\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width,initial-scale=1.0,minimum-scale=1.0,maximum-scale=1.0\">\n<meta name=\"description\" content=\"青森県八戸市にある株式会社清掃センターです。下水道管路施設維持管理、土木工事一般、ビル管理、処理施設等の運転管理等を行っています。\" />\n<meta name=\"keywords\" content=\"青森県,八戸市,清掃センター,下水道,土木工事,ビル管理,施設運転管理,路面・道路清掃\" />\n<meta name=\"format-detection\" content=\"telephone=no\">\n\n<meta http-equiv=\"Content-Script-Type\" content=\"text/javascript\" />\n<meta http-equiv=\"Content-Style-Type\" content=\"text/css\" />\n\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"http://www.seisou-center.co.jp/wp/wp-content/themes/seisou-center/css/base.css\">\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"http://www.seisou-center.co.jp/wp/wp-content/themes/seisou-center/css/pc.css\" media=\"screen and (min-width:896px),print\">\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"http://www.seisou-center.co.jp/wp/wp-content/themes/seisou-center/css/sp.css\" media=\"screen and (max-width:895px)\">\n\n<script type=\"text/javascript\"  src=\"http://www.seisou-center.co.jp/wp/wp-content/themes/seisou-center/js/jquery-1.11.2.min.js\"></script>\n<script type=\"text/javascript\"  src=\"http://www.seisou-center.co.jp/wp/wp-content/themes/seisou-center/js/jquery.easing.1.3.js\"></script>\n\n<script type=\"text/javascript\"  src=\"http://www.seisou-center.co.jp/wp/wp-content/themes/seisou-center/js/base.js\"></script>\n<script type=\"text/javascript\"  src=\"http://www.seisou-center.co.jp/wp/wp-content/themes/seisou-center/js/common.js\"></script>\n\n\t\t<script type=\"text/javascript\">\n\t\t\twindow._wpemojiSettings = {\"baseUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/s.w.org\\/images\\/core\\/emoji\\/12.0.0-1\\/72x72\\/\",\"ext\":\".png\",\"svgUrl\":false,\"svgExt\":\".svg\",\"source\":{\"concatemoji\":\"http:\\/\\/www.seisou-center.co.jp\\/wp\\/wp-includes\\/js\\/wp-emoji-release.min.js?ver=5.3.21\"}};\n\t\t\t